WEBVTT

00:02:56.986 --> 00:03:00.372
about the past, the present
and the future of time,

00:03:00.396 --> 00:03:04.515
as it relates to the combating
of racism and white dominance.

00:03:04.997 --> 00:03:06.977
First: the past.

00:03:07.802 --> 00:03:09.689
Time has a history,

00:03:09.713 --> 00:03:11.680
and so do black people.

00:03:11.704 --> 00:03:14.370
But we treat time as though
it is timeless,

00:03:14.394 --> 00:03:16.798
as though it has always been this way,

00:03:16.822 --> 00:03:19.111
as though it doesn't have
a political history

00:03:19.135 --> 00:03:21.345
bound up with the plunder
of indigenous lands,

00:03:21.369 --> 00:03:23.318
the genocide of indigenous people

00:03:23.342 --> 00:03:25.992
and the stealing of Africans
from their homeland.

